These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, go, monopoly
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower, poppy, zinnia
1. the person playing go is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
3. the person who growspoppy is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the person playing go##6
5. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | monopoly  | mah-jongg | go | snooker  |
| Flower   | dahlia | poppy   | zinnia  | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rugby, lacrosse, rowing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, siglo, game, montecristo
1. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the montecristo-smoker##8
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
3. the person who's sport is soccer is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is rugby##2
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the swisher-smoker##7
6. the game-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
7. the swisher-smoker is not to the left of the swisher-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Sport   | lacrosse | rugby          | rowing | soccer     |
| Cigar    | game      | montecristo | swisher | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, papaya, apricot, broccoli
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, climbing, skiing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person eating apricot##8
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating orange##1
4. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
5. the person eating broccoli is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
7. the person eating broccoli is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food           | orange | papaya | apricot     | broccoli |
| Sport   | climbing    | badminton   | sailing | skiing    |

