.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, old-henry, pall-mall, oliveros
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, august, september
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##8
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
5. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | pall-mall   | old-henry         | oliveros   | prince    |
| Birthday         | march | september | august | january |

