.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, disco, trance, d&b
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, turquise, ivory, green
1. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of disco##7
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
3. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of trance and the fan of hip-hop##7
4. the fan of trance is not to the left of the person who likes green##8
5. the person who likes green is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person who likes turquise##7
6. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
7. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
8. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance | d&b | hip-hop    |
| Color         | apricot | green   | ivory   | turquise |

