.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, june, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, cricket, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
6. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##8
7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday          | december | january | october  | june |
| Sport   | basketball   | lacrosse         | cricket | volleyball |

