.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, security-guard, police-officer, analyst
4 different pets are kept: dog, rat, fish, frog
1. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the security-guard##8
2. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the analyst and the owner of the fish##7
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
4. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
5. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the security-guard##8
6. the fisherman is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
8. the fisherman is on the left of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job   | security-guard      | police-officer | fisherman | analyst   |
| Pet      | dog | fish | frog  | rat |

