.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, november, december
City: boston, hamburg, liverpool, paris
1. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person traveling to paris##8
2. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's birthday is in august##7
5. the person who's birthday is in november is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
6. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's birthday is in november##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Birthday     | august | november | december | march     |
| City   | boston   | liverpool        | paris          | hamburg |

