There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, pakistani, dutch, indian
1. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking milk and the nigerian##2
2. the indian is on the far left##1
3. the indian is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
5. the pakistani is the pakistani##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is not the dutch##6
7. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
8. the nigerian is not to the left of the pakistani##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage   | milk   | coffee | soy-milk | tea |
| Nationality     | indian | pakistani       | nigerian  | dutch    |

