3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the fan of trance##1
4. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
5. the fan of indie is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the fan of trance##7
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
8. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
