.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skiing, badminton, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, snowmobile, ship
 1. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the roller##8
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 7. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 9. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##8
10. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person driving the skateboard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | skiing    | badminton | sailing | baseball |
| Transport   | skateboard | ship  | snowmobile     | roller    |

