.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, videographer, dressmaker, analyst
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, orange, brown, lavender
1. the person who likes orange is not the freelancer##6
2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the analyst is not to the left of the person who likes lavender##8
4. the dressmaker is the person who likes turquise##1
5. the analyst is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who likes turquise##7
6. the analyst is on the left of the freelancer##1
7. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes lavender and the dressmaker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | videographer    | analyst | freelancer | dressmaker |
| Color   | orange | lavender      | brown     | turquise     |

 